        {
          "abilityId": 101,
          "accessMode": "ro",
          "code": "MachineStatus",
          "description": "\"\"\"待机、充电、割草、暂停、回站、升级、定点割草、错误、自检、充电带工作、急停（增加提示语：请在机器上解除急停）、锁屏\n\n注意：只有待机和充电状态下可以修改APP对应的预约、分区、设置参数，其他状态都不允许修改参数\n\"\"\n\"\n",
          "description2": "Standby, Charging, Lawn Mowing, Pause, Return to Station, Upgrade, Fixed-Point Lawn Mowing, Error, Self-Check, Charging with Working Module, Emergency Stop (with added prompt: Please release emergency stop on the device), Lock Screen\n\nNote: Only in standby and charging states can the corresponding reservation, partition, and settings parameters of the APP be modified. Parameter modification is not allowed in other states.\n\n\n\n",
          "name": "机器状态",
          "typeSpec": {
            "type": "enum",
            "range": [
              "STANDBY",
              "CHARGING",
              "MOWING",
              "PAUSED",
              "PARK",
              "UPDATA",
              "FIXED_MOWING",
              "ERROR",
              "SELF_TEST",
              "CHARGING_WITH_TASK_SUSPEND",
              "EMERGENCY",
              "LOCKED"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "abilityId": 102,
          "accessMode": "ro",
          "code": "MachineError",
          "description": "\"倾斜小于24、倾斜大于35、无边界信号、左电机堵转、右电机堵转、电池电压高、电池温度异常、放电错误、充电过温、电池损坏、电池电压低、放电过流、放电过温、充电电压低、电池异常需重启，IMU失效、边界传感器失效、雨水失效、霍尔失效、机器倾斜、机器出界、机器提升、机器受困、割草电机故障、机器倾覆、电机过流、电机霍尔错误、电机板通信异常、边界检测通讯异常、电机错误\n\"\n",
          "description2": "Tilt less than 24°, tilt greater than 35°, no boundary signal, left motor stalled, right motor stalled, high battery voltage, abnormal battery temperature, discharge error, overheating during charging, battery damage, low battery voltage, overcurrent during discharge, overheating during discharge, low charging voltage, battery malfunction requiring restart, IMU failure, boundary sensor failure, rain failure, Hall effect sensor failure, machine tilt, machine out of bounds, machine lifting, machine stuck, lawnmower motor malfunction, machine overturning, motor overcurrent, motor Hall effect sensor error, motor board communication malfunction, boundary detection communication malfunction, motor error\n\n\n",
          "extensions": {
            "scope": "fault"
          },
          "name": "机器错误",
          "typeSpec": {
            "type": "bitmap",
            "label": [
              "FAULT_LEAN",
              "FAULT_TOO_STEEP",
              "NO_SIGNAL",
